{"tid":82481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得Facebook好鬼","createTime":"2017-01-16T03:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T01:49:40.000Z","uid":37894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef37bdf509f707d035d7a8db76ee8ba21979bc3f","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n我女朋友想開個分身account 要黎玩Facebook d game<br />\n<br />\n咁佢個妹咁岩係英國，有張英國號碼既電話卡<br />\n<br />\n而我就有一部公司既垃圾電話，部機平時淨係要黎收公司Whatsapp, 無其他用途<br />\n<br />\n我女朋友就拎左我部公司機裝左個Facebook app,同埋用佢妹個英國電話號碼開左個分身<br />\n<br />\n但一開完Facebook 既suggestion friends近七成都係佢正account 內既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打試過或者知道點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938feb4d8e8228e12a06157bfe00207c3a8a5ece","tid":82481,"uid":29751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"係咪通訊錄入面有佢正account D人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3b06143f15328081c64728b934c95eefdef893","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪通訊錄入面有佢正account D人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無，部機係我既公司機，得我而家d同事既電話"},{"pid":"05052bbcbea5d7fa34e06a77922d30cf21a7d319","tid":82481,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:45:30.000Z","msg":"佢啲friend都有玩隻game?"},{"pid":"730dd820767dbd7b9d6af369a850c34eeb23e552","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢啲friend都有玩隻game?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無呀，係一開完account果刻Facebook已經即刻叫佢add返正身既朋友<br />\n但果陣game都未開咁點會知呢，呢下先覺得好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" cla