ve contact.  如果係你女友， 電話又有相關contact,  裝game唔小心click左permit access contact list,  就玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c04865d5ab725b48eeff4568011138d28e9493","tid":82481,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"他不是他 是另一個他"},{"pid":"0a99ad9f30b3f48013a79333ab620ecd92c9e51e","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你女友啊妹張卡註冊咗你女友啊妹個FB,跟住你女友啊妹add咗你女友正ac嘅fd,跟住FB就 suggest 咗你女友個正ac d fd比你女友新開個ac？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我女朋友正account都無add佢個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而張電話卡個號碼係普通英國遊客卡黎"},{"pid":"e988ef777b46da001e735b92fbe4f32f583eb083","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常係access到電話contact list先做到呢個效果， 隻game係裝係你女人電話定你電話？如果係你電話，咩contact都冇， 應該唔會get到relative contact.  如果係你女友， 電話又有相關contact,  裝game唔小心click左permit access contact list,  就玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻game裝係女友電話，但新Facebook account 就用我公司電話部機開既，我部公司機自己都好少用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇怪點解會咁"},{"pid":"85624ba2cb628eee1d3ca7194ca1eae2aca29b40","tid":82481,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"咁神奇，新號碼新手提都可以relate 返啲舊朋友"},{"pid":"527537eb340a3f5694082bf6d38eeb306810a8d9","tid":82481,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩FB仲DETECT到我相簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19020b7a