b43772056a4b997507425b4f403d910d0ce7e88","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n都唔係咩新聞<br />\n而家呢個世界根本無privacy可言</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左監聽我都諗唔到有咩可能可以將兩個戶口link埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係唔知邊度比咗permission你唔記得姐<br />\n監聽唔係新聞，但係應該無先進到個個 user都咁樣用法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩permission係會咁樣連結到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個公司電話係D老爺機黎，仲要係我剛剛轉新工無耐公司俾我既，我無用過呢部機Whatsapp或者打過俾女友<br />\n<br />\n而個新Facebook account 係直接使用英國電話號碼註冊既，同我或者女朋友都係香港，無直接關係<br />\n<br />\n所以先覺得好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c76151a602c1aa5762486a6f74bcf7d505f8e5","tid":82481,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5d13ca0fc44a86513b5e7f4bd26061e8ebd85ae","tid":82481,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a950c9a9a966c4023118d403bc3826037abec206","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開過幾次分身都冇呢個問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算add返本來個ac都好少suggest嗰個ac嘅朋友俾分身<br />\n會唔會個game之前連過你女朋友個正ac, 再連落分身嗰時fb detect到係同一個用戶所以有嗰堆suggestions?<br />\n<br />\n利申: it白痴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴晚係想整左個Facebook account 先再搞其他野<br />\n<br />\n同埋我講清楚d啦，其實女友主要想開分身黎like自己d野，咪有好多Facebook 活動係要鬥多like既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以不存在有無裝game既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82026f7a47c1c235ebf0785d31acb680d449b01","tid":82481,"uid":11257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"Ig都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142b7105d0bca4297f98c8021884beb1e68c1ae8","tid":82481,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"Facebook會問/要求存取其他人程式嘅資料<br />\n你不如問吓卡主佢有冇accept過仲好啦"},{"pid":"76d2668f8498944c9543f7b74d8880b53006550d","tid":82481,"uid":56614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"覺 識左啲新朋友之後就會見到facebook推薦我add佢地 一直都覺得好奇怪 明明冇共同朋友又冇其他有關係嘅野"},{"pid":"e0f5229d73a3d16f677c537514bc74eaccfae2ee","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺 識左啲新朋友之後就會見到facebook推薦我add佢地 一直都覺得好奇怪 明明冇共同朋友又冇其他有關係嘅野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我反而覺得有解，因為我都試過<br />\n雖然set左facebook 唔可以access我既電話聯絡人，但我覺得佢係應該知左我個手提電話<br />\n<br />\n當新朋友save左我電話果陣佢就可以suggest個新朋友去我Facebook<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179f2177aea77e53495cb889eb356a4006c83e0a","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Facebook會問/要求存取其他人程式嘅資料<br />\n你不如問吓卡主佢有冇accept過仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電話卡主遠在歐遊多時，唔會有我女朋友d新同事電話，<br />\n再者，有都應該suggest電話卡主即係阿妹既朋友俾我女朋友個分身掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0eaf3f0da7b9ef5ce8a72b3c4c106256874ef2c","tid":82481,"uid":18249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"iPhone 定位個啲<br />\n可能因為兩個人經常係同一範圍佢又detect到<br />\n鳩估"},{"pid":"c1dee6211d128438a87061433f6ba8eb647c2840","tid":82481,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iPhone 定位個啲<br />\n可能因為兩個人經常係同一範圍佢又detect到<br />\n鳩估</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我部三叔s5應該無能力（應該係話無電力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）容許佢24小時scan住我去邊<br />\n<br />\n女朋友用iPhone,而妹妹人在歐洲多時"},{"pid":"9d221838b2d737fb89330f58d3d30edeeb701762","tid":82481,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"反向，你部機無資料，但佢會係人哋嘅通訊錄到搵你嘅資料，再睇下佢哋嘅共同朋友圈，加地區去推測，你女朋友嘅資料都會乎合到前一個帳戶嘅共通點，所以無乜岀奇<br />\n<br />\n你自己唔岀賣自己，但點都有啲蛛絲馬跡畀人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138397c3c76c41d3161ba2759ef9e9ed59bb15a3","tid":82481,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"鬼到爆 掌控全球幾億人既資訊"}]}